				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Gothric Rillyn has been buried underground by Minsc after he tried to rob him. Player can hear muffled yelling from the grave and try to dig him out. This dialogue opens with Gothric having just pulled himself out of the hole (we don't see this in cinematic) and is now dusting himself down."
				}
